## Debugging

### Enable Debug Logging

Set `DEBUG=true` in environment:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{server-name}}": {
      "env": {
        "DEBUG": "true"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Use MCP Inspector

```bash
npm run inspect
```

This opens an interactive inspector to test tools without Claude.

